# Troubleshooting

## Issue 1: Wazuh Agent Not Connecting
### Problem
The Windows agent failed to appear in the Wazuh dashboard.

### Fix
- Restarted Wazuh services
- Verified IP connectivity
- Reconfigured agent enrollment

---

## Issue 2: VirtualBox Network Problems
### Problem
Kali Linux could not communicate with Windows Server.

### Fix
- Added Host-Only adapters
- Verified IP addresses
- Enabled cable connection in VirtualBox settings

---

## Issue 3: Wazuh Enrollment Failure
### Problem
Agent registration failed on port 1515.

### Fix
- Enabled authd
- Restarted Wazuh manager
- Re-enrolled the agent

---

## Issue 4: Dashboard Access Problems
### Problem
Wazuh dashboard could not be reached from the host machine.

### Fix
- Configured Host-Only networking
- Assigned internal IP addresses
- Verified browser access
